LIMIT 5 OFFSET 5;

👉 Meaning:

Skip first 5 records
Show next 5 records
Example 3: Pagination (Very Important)
Page calculation
Page 1 → OFFSET 0
Page 2 → OFFSET 5
Page 3 → OFFSET 10
Query
SELECT * FROM Employee
LIMIT 5 OFFSET 10;

👉 Shows page 3 data (records 11–15)

